  "firstAcquaintance": "An energetic young succubus who accidentally drew the Holy Sword and set out on the path of a knight.",
  "personality": "Young, cheerful, vibrant, and alluring -- as if radiating warm sunshine. A natural-born leader.",
  "like": "The Holy Sword, weapon maintenance",
  "familiarData": "Yasena is the daughter of the great succubus \"Morgan Le Fay,\" born into a post-war world filled with slaves.\nWith the succubus nation established, the new generation of succubi no longer needed to struggle for sustenance. Born in this era, Yasena had no need to learn succubus abilities. Instead, she was deeply influenced by her knight father and developed a strong interest in chivalry.\nAfter the war, captured kingdom weapons were placed under succubus custody. Yasena grew up tending to the legendary Holy Sword that only a hero could draw. Upon coming of age, she successfully drew the Holy Sword and embarked on the path to fulfill her dream -- the liberation of slaves.\nHaving seen her father kept as a slave by the succubi, Yasena dreamed of changing the lives of slaves. She was moved by a certain honorary demon citizen's \"Soul Freedom\" speech and came to the guild hoping to study under that person.\n\nShe seems to have some connection with the succubus proprietress of the candy shop across the street, but the owner flusteredly denies it.",
